# Git LFS tracking for the bundled kraken model weights.
#
# These are large binary files (5MB + 16MB) that are embedded into the app
# binary at compile time via `include_bytes!`. LFS keeps them out of the regular
# git history (which stays small + fast to clone) while still making them
# available to CI and anyone who clones the repo.
#
# One-time local setup (run after `brew install git-lfs`):
#   git lfs install
#   git lfs track "kraken-models/*.safetensors"
#   # (the line above is what this file records — re-running it is a no-op)
#   git add .gitattributes
#   git add kraken-models/bur_segment.safetensors kraken-models/bur_recog.safetensors
#   git commit -m "Track kraken models via Git LFS"
kraken-models/*.safetensors filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
